# Single source of truth for the cloud environment every routine deploys to.
#
# The deploy process — the `deploy-routine-changes` skill (interactive) and the
# `deploy-routines` GHA prompt (when its CI token is unblocked) — reads
# ENVIRONMENT_ID from here and sets `job_config.ccr.environment_id` on every
# RemoteTrigger create/update. Pin it here once; never repeat the id elsewhere.
#
# The environment's CONTENTS — GH_OWNER, GH_TOKEN, and other secrets — live ONLY
# in the cloud environment (claude.ai), never in this repo. This file pins WHICH
# environment, not WHAT is in it.
#
# Format: KEY=VALUE, one per line. Read with:
#   grep -m1 '^ENVIRONMENT_ID=' routines/_common/deploy.config | cut -d= -f2 | tr -d '\r'
ENVIRONMENT_ID=env_01GVXvvN64GtSjsfhychXy7m
